OL,3,CMan, 20, dies after crash on A1M in
OL,4,CCounty Durham
OL,6,FA man has died after a car crash on
OL,7,Fthe A1M in County Durham.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Fincident on the northbound carriageway
OL,11,Fbetween Junction 62 , Carrville, and
OL,12,F63, Chester-le-Street, at around
OL,13,F10.50pm on Sunday 26 April.
OL,15,FDurham Police believe a black Mercedes
OL,16,FA-Class struck the central reservation
OL,17,Fbefore coming to rest on its roof.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
