OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1777317067
OL,3,CMan, 20, dies after crash on A1M in
OL,4,CCounty Durham
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man sustained critical
OL,7,Finjuries and died at the scene. His
OL,8,Ffamily have been informed and are
OL,9,Fbeing supported by specialist officers.
OL,11,FA second man, also aged 20, sustained
OL,12,Flife-threatening injuries and was
OL,13,Ftaken to the Royal Victoria Infirmary
OL,14,Fin Newcastle. His condition is
OL,15,Fdescribed as critical.
OL,17,FA third man sustained serious injuries
OL,18,Fand was taken to the same hospital
OL,19,Fwhere he remains in a stable condition.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
