OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1777317067
OL,3,CMan, 20, dies after crash on A1M in
OL,4,CCounty Durham
OL,6,FThe road was closed for over 12 hours
OL,7,Fand reopened shortly after 12.30pm on
OL,8,FMonday.
OL,10,FPolice are appealing for witnesses and
OL,11,Fsay they would like to speak to anyone
OL,12,Fwho may have dashcam footage of the
OL,13,Fvehicle prior to the incident.
OL,15,FAnyone with any information should
OL,16,Fcontact the force on 101.
